description: "Imagine the food you love, bite-sized bursting with flavor." That's what we are all about. Forget about burgers, buns, dogs and taco shells. Think DUMPlings-N-Spring ROLLs. We create dumplings and spring rolls inspired by cultures, by you, me, the past and present. Are you a vegan, vegetarian, gluten-free, low carb, young, old or somewhere in between? Whatever it is, we have something for you. We are providing quality sustenance, affordability, convenience, creativity and originality all in one package. Dump-N-Roll is on a mission, to be Philly’s Next Best Food truck. You can come to us and we can cater to you. Beyond feeding hungry bellies lies our core mission. It’s to give our time back to the community, to the people, to the places and things that matter and make an impact big or small. Mainly our focus are on the seeds of the future. The generations of tomorrow.
name: Dump-N-Roll
